y available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/setSinkId\"><code>setSinkId()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/abort_event\"><code>abort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplay_event\"><code>canplay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplaythrough_event\"><code>canplaythrough</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/durationchange_event\"><code>durationchange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/emptied_event\"><code>emptied</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\"><code>ended</code></a></li><li><em><code>error</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadeddata_event\"><code>loadeddata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadedmetadata_event\"><code>loadedmetadata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause_event\"><code>pause</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/play_event\"><code>play</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\"><code>playing</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/progress_event\"><code>progress</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ratechange_event\"><code>ratechange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeked_event\"><code>seeked</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeking_event\"><code>seeking</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/stalled_event\"><code>stalled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/suspend_event\"><code>suspend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/timeupdate_event\"><code>timeupdate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/volumechange_event\"><code>volumechange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/waiting_event\"><code>waiting</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"**`error`** イベントは、リソースがエラーのために読み込めなかったときに発生します（例えば、ネットワーク接続の問題など）。\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n      <td>なし</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n      <td>不可</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n## 例\n\n```js\nconst video = document.querySelector('video');\nconst videoSrc = 'https://path/to/video.webm';\n\nvideo.addEventListener('error', () =&gt; {\n  console.error(`Error loading: ${videoSrc}`);\n});\n\nvideo.setAttribute('src', videoSrc);\n```\n\n## 仕様書"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#event-media-error","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLMediaElement.error_event"}},{"type":"prose","valu